Sedna version 0.01
=====================

This module implements the Perl bindings for the Sedna XML database.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Sedna XML database to be installed on either
/usr/lib/sedna or /usr/local/sedna with a shared object available
(which might not be the default compilation option).

